data.description:
Two bedroom, one bathroom house for rent in Parker, Idaho. Small town setting near Sand Dunes, St. Anthony Sand Bar, and only 15 minutes from Rexburg. Both bedrooms boast large closets, and the bathroom has built-in floor to ceiling cabinets. Stacking washer and dryer included. Property has a large front yard with mature trees and the beginnings of a raspberry patch. Pictures show furnishings, but house will be rented unfurnished unless other arrangements are made.

Tenant responsible for utilities.
